+ * <tr><td> {@code 42 μs} </td><td> {@code @Timeout(value = 42, unit = MICROSECONDS)} </td></tr>
+ * <tr><td> {@code 42 ms} </td><td> {@code @Timeout(value = 42, unit = MILLISECONDS)} </td></tr>
+ * <tr><td> {@code 42 s}  </td><td> {@code @Timeout(value = 42, unit = SECONDS)}      </td></tr>
